24 Jul 2022 | 03:14 PM UTC
Canada: Police responding to reports of shooting incident near Longhorn Saloon in Whistler, B.C., July 24
FLASH: Police responding to reports of shooting incident near Longhorn Saloon in Whistler, B.C., Canada, July 24; avoid the area.
Critical
transportation
security
CAN
EventPolice are responding to reports of a shooting incident near the Longhorn Saloon in Whistler, British Columbia, July 24. Authorities did not immediately confirm further details regarding the incident, including the number of associated casualties.Heightened security and localized transport disruptions are likely in the area over the coming hours.This is a developing situation; additional information will be issued as warranted.AdviceAvoid the affected area and maintain heightened vigilance if operating in Whistler July 24. Consider taking alternative routes to circumvent the incident site. Adhere to all instructions issued by local authorities.
